graph TB
    User([User Input]) --> InputLayer
    
    subgraph InputLayer [INPUT FILTERING — 4 Layers]
        L1[Layer 1: OpenAI Moderation API<br/>FREE — blocks harmful content]
        L1 -->|Pass| L2[Layer 2: PII Detection<br/>Presidio — 30+ entity types]
        L2 -->|Redact PII| L3[Layer 3: Injection Sanitization<br/>Regex + pattern matching]
        L3 -->|Clean| L4[Layer 4: Risk Classification<br/>SAFE / SUSPICIOUS / MALICIOUS]
    end
    
    L1 -->|Blocked| SafeResponse
    L4 -->|MALICIOUS| SafeResponse[Safe Fallback:<br/>I can only help with...]
    
    L4 -->|SAFE| LLM
    L4 -->|SUSPICIOUS| LLM_Cautious[LLM with extra warning<br/>in system prompt]
    
    subgraph LLM [LLM Processing]
        SystemPrompt[System Prompt<br/>with Instruction Hierarchy<br/>Level 1: immutable<br/>Level 2: admin<br/>Level 3: user]
        Canary[Canary Token<br/>hidden tripwire string]
        Context[RAG Context<br/>grounded in documents only]
        SystemPrompt --> Generate[Generate Response]
        Canary --> Generate
        Context --> Generate
    end
    
    LLM_Cautious --> Generate
    
    Generate --> OutputLayer
    
    subgraph OutputLayer [OUTPUT FILTERING]
        O1[Canary Check<br/>Did the secret string leak?]
        O1 -->|Clean| O2[PII Output Scan<br/>Catch any PII in response]
        O2 -->|Clean| O3[Policy Check<br/>Domain-specific rules]
        O3 -->|Clean| O4[Hallucination Check<br/>Claims supported by context?]
    end
    
    O1 -->|LEAKED| SafeResponse
    O2 -->|PII Found| Redact[Redact from output]
    O3 -->|Violation| SafeResponse
    O4 -->|Unsupported claims| AddDisclaimer[Add uncertainty disclaimer]
    
    Redact --> PII_Reinsert
    O4 -->|All supported| PII_Reinsert[Re-insert real PII<br/>for the user only]
    AddDisclaimer --> PII_Reinsert
    
    PII_Reinsert --> AuditLog[Audit Log<br/>metadata only — no PII stored]
    SafeResponse --> AuditLog
    
    AuditLog --> Response([Response to User])
    
    subgraph Monitoring
        BiasTest[Monthly: Bias Audit<br/>Same prompt + different demographics]
        RedTeam[Quarterly: Red Team<br/>15+ attack vectors]
        Faithfulness[Weekly: Faithfulness Sampling<br/>1% of traffic scored]
    end
    
    AuditLog -.-> Monitoring

    style InputLayer fill:#1a1a2e,color:#fff
    style OutputLayer fill:#1a1a2e,color:#fff
    style L1 fill:#3fb950,color:#fff
    style L2 fill:#1f6feb,color:#fff
    style L3 fill:#8957e5,color:#fff
    style L4 fill:#d29922,color:#fff
    style SafeResponse fill:#da3633,color:#fff
    style Canary fill:#d29922,color:#fff
    style AuditLog fill:#3fb950,color:#fff
